responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "64584FFD4E09008BE22663950A9AB2BF", "We have both set foot upon good fortune! It is not always easy, if at all, to encounter my Caravan of Curiosities unless we have business of grim tidings to share. Let us enjoy this spot of nothingness. Our own bit of the void, some would say.")
